(84, 1, '2020-12-08 22:08:25', '2020-12-08 22:08:25', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>2.5GHz (up to 4.5GHz) Intel Core i5-10300H processor and 8GB of DDR4 RAM can easily run the latest AAA titles</li>\r\n 	<li>512GB PCIe solid state drive (SSD) offers sufficient storage for your games, software, movies, and more</li>\r\n 	<li>4GB NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1650 Ti is a graphics powerhouse that renders every detail so you can experience every game to its fullest</li>\r\n 	<li>15.6\" FHD screen with a native resolution of 1920 x 1080 and 144Hz refresh rate delivers stunning visuals and is also equipped with anti-glare to relieve stress on your eyes</li>\r\n 	<li>Integrated 10/100/1000 ethernet port and Wi-Fi 6 (Gig+) 2x2 let you access high-speed networks</li>\r\n 	<li>Bluetooth 5.0 can pair with external input/output devices such as a wireless mouse and keyboard, Bluetooth speakers, headsets, and more</li>\r\n 	<li>48Wh 3-cell lithium-ion battery packs ample battery life so you can delve into your favourite games on-the-go</li>\r\n 	<li>USB 3.2 Gen 2 Type-C port, three USB 3.2 Gen 1 Type-A ports, HDMI display port, 3.5mm combo jack, and RJ-45 port let you connect a wide range of devices and peripherals such as your keyboard, mouse, external storage, smartphones, router, and more</li>\r\n 	<li>Aura RGB backlit gaming keyboard illuminates every key for convenient operation in dimly lit areas</li>\r\n 	<li>Preloaded with bilingual Windows 10 64-bit operating system that comes with security upgrades and an enhanced user interface</li>\r\n</ul>', 'ASUS ROG Strix G15 15.6\" Gaming Laptop (Intel Core i5-10300H/512GB SSD/8GB RAM/GeForce GTX 1650 Ti)', '<div class=\"productDescription_2cw7s withChatInitiator_2G7gG\">\r\n<div class=\"description_39c9o\">Built for intense gaming, the ASUS ROG Strix G15 is rigged with a powerful Intel Core i5 processor, 8GB of RAM, and a powerful GTX 1650 Ti GPU. It features a 15.6\" Full HD display equipped with anti-glare and a 144Hz refresh rate for smooth and fluid motion visuals. The laptop also comes with a 512GB solid state drive and an Aura RGB backlit keyboard.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"initiator_17su9\" data-automation=\"blue-shirt-chat-container\">\r\n<div class=\"blueShirtsChatContainer_3uHKv\"></div>\r\n</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'asus-rog-strix-g15-15-6-gaming-laptop-intel-core-i5-10300h-512gb-ssd-8gb-ram-geforce-gtx-1650-ti', '', '', '2020-12-08 22:14:36', '2020-12-08 22:14:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=84', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(86, 1, '2020-12-08 22:13:39', '2020-12-08 22:13:39', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>10th Generation Intel Core i5-1035G4 quad-core processor and 8GB of LPDDR4-3200 SDRAM can power through multi-tasking with ease</li>\r\n 	<li>512GB solid state drive provides ample room to store your files, photos, documents, and more, plus rapid read and write times mean faster access to everything stored on it</li>\r\n 	<li>32GB of Intel Optane memory optimizes your workflow by speeding up access times to frequently used applications</li>\r\n 	<li>13.3\" IPS FHD (1920 x 1080) BrightView micro-edge WLED-backlit multitouch-enabled display with Corning Gorilla Glass NBT is bright, clear, and allows you to interact with programs via tapping and touchscreen gestures</li>\r\n 	<li>Intel Wi-Fi 6 AX 201 (2 x 2) and Bluetooth 5 wireless with MU-MIMO support connectivity lets you connect to networks and pair accessories to your laptop without any tangles of wires</li>\r\n 	<li>4 cell 60.67Wh lithium-ion battery delivers hours of use so you can stay productive plus with a weight of just 2.87lbs it\'s portable enough to take with you wherever you need to go</li>\r\n 	<li>2 x USB 3.1 Gen 2 Type-C with Thunderbolt port, USB 3.1 Gen 1 Type-A with HP Sleep and Charge port, HDMI 2.0 port, DisplayPort 1.4 jack, and a headphone-microphone combo port allow you to connect many different kinds of accesories and additional screens</li>\r\n 	<li>HP TrueVision HD IR webcam with integrated dual array digital microphones helps you stay connected to friends and family with crisp, clear visuals and stellar audio quality during calls, plus a webcam kill switch, HP Sure View privacy screen and microphone mute button help ensure your privacy</li>\r\n 	<li>Bang &amp; Olufsen dual speakers deliver high-quality audio to enjoy movies and music to their fullest extant</li>\r\n 	<li>2-in-1 design works as both a tablet and laptop for flexibility and adaptibility to whatever use cases you require</li>\r\n 	<li>HP Digital Pen stylus allows you to interact with the touch surface and applications in novel ways</li>\r\n 	<li>Preinstalled with Windows 10 Home, with helpful apps installed by default, an improved Start menu, and many more usability features</li>\r\n</ul>', 'HP 13.3\" Touchscreen 2-in-1 Laptop - Natural Silver Aluminum (Intel Core i5-1035G4/512GB SSD/8GB RAM/Windows 10)', '<div class=\"productDescription_2cw7s withChatInitiator_2G7gG\">\r\n<div class=\"description_39c9o\">Get great computing perfomance in a flexible, portable package with the HP 13.3\" touchscreen 2-in-1 laptop. Its Intel Core i5-1035G4 processor and 8GB of RAM can power through multi-tasking without a problem, and its tablet-to-laptop convertability makes it suitable for all kinds of work from word processing to sketching.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"initiator_17su9\" data-automation=\"blue-shirt-chat-container\">\r\n<div class=\"blueShirtsChatContainer_3uHKv\"></div>\r\n</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'hp-13-3-touchscreen-2-in-1-laptop-natural-silver-aluminum-intel-core-i5-1035g4-512gb-ssd-8gb-ram-windows-10', '', '', '2020-12-08 22:23:11', '2020-12-08 22:23:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=86', 0, 'product', '', 0),
