(118, 1, '2020-12-08 22:43:33', '2020-12-08 22:43:33', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>65\" screen with 4K Ultra HD resolution of 3840 x 2160 pixels takes your breath away with its stunning images in clear and crisp detail</li>\r\n 	<li>4K UHD processor upscales all your favourite content so you can view it in 4K Ultra HD clarity</li>\r\n 	<li>Quantum Dot technology can produce more than a billion shades of colour with 100% colour volume to display rich life-like colours</li>\r\n 	<li>Dual LED backlighting with Quantum HDR enhances contrast ratios so you can see deeper blacks and brighter images</li>\r\n 	<li>MR120 motion rate minimises blur during fast-paced scenes and smooths them to improve the video clarity</li>\r\n 	<li>Adaptive Sound Optimizer with Audio Scenic Intelligence technology scans the content being played and optimises the audio output to match the scene</li>\r\n 	<li>20W dual channel speakers produce crisp and deep sound to match the high-quality visuals</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Samsung 65\" 4K UHD HDR QLED Tizen Smart TV (QN65Q6DTAFXZC) - 2020 - Titan Grey', '<div class=\"col-xs-12_1GBy8 col-sm-6_9CRts col-md-8_3iF9f productContent_nzEog\">\r\n<div class=\"overviewContainer_2Ohq3 greaterThanSmall_3cTlu\">\r\n<div class=\"productDescription_2cw7s\">\r\n<div class=\"description_39c9o\">Pushing the boundaries of entertainment, the Samsung Q6DT smart TV delivers stunning picture quality and cutting-edge intelligence. It boasts a 65\" QLED screen with 4K Ultra HD resolution and a dual-LED system that showcases awe-inspiring visuals with natural-looking colours. This smart TV is powered by Tizen, offering easy control, loads of streaming apps, and other features.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12_1GBy8 col-sm-6_9CRts col-md-4_2WnBH collapseColContainer_ueBNu\">\r\n<div class=\"pricingContainer_25k3c\">\r\n<div class=\"productPricingContainer_3gTS3\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'samsung-65-4k-uhd-hdr-qled-tizen-smart-tv-qn65q6dtafxzc-2020-titan-grey', '', '', '2020-12-08 22:45:17', '2020-12-08 22:45:17', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=118', 0, 'product', '', 0),
