(120, 1, '2020-12-08 22:44:58', '2020-12-08 22:44:58', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>65-inch LED screen lets you experience movies and shows on a powerful display in stunning clarity</li>\r\n 	<li>4K Ultra HD resolution (3840 x 2160) delivers clear, crisp pictures in vivid hues</li>\r\n 	<li>High Dynamic Range (HDR) displays a wide range of shades, showcasing true-to-life colours even in dark scenes</li>\r\n 	<li>MR120 motion rate reduces blur, lag, and streaks so you can enjoy smooth, crisp action sequences in stunning clarity</li>\r\n 	<li>AI scene recognition technology automatically identifies the input content, then adjusts the picture and sound to optimise your viewing experience</li>\r\n 	<li>Android TV operating system gives you the freedom to access a large collection of apps containing movies and series</li>\r\n 	<li>Preloaded with Netflix, YouTube, Amazon Prime, and Disney + (subscriptions may be required, sold separately), so you can stream your favourite shows and movies</li>\r\n 	<li>Built-in Google Assistant and compatibility with Amazon Alexa lets you gain quick access to your favourite shows and control the television using your voice</li>\r\n 	<li>Bluetooth connectivity lets you wirelessly pair the TV with peripheral audio devices like a soundbar or headphones</li>\r\n 	<li>Wi-Fi and wired internet connectivity options allow you to connect this TV with your home network</li>\r\n 	<li>Three HDMI 2.0 and two USB 2.0 ports let you connect the TV to speakers, media storage devices, DVD and Blu-Ray players, and more</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Hisense 65\" 4K UHD HDR LED Android Smart TV (65H78G) - 2020', '<div class=\"col-xs-12_1GBy8 col-sm-6_9CRts col-md-8_3iF9f productContent_nzEog\">\r\n<div class=\"overviewContainer_2Ohq3 greaterThanSmall_3cTlu\">\r\n<div class=\"productDescription_2cw7s\">\r\n<div class=\"description_39c9o\">Enhance your home entertainment set up with this 65\" Hisense smart TV. With its 4K Ultra HD display, this television lets you enjoy your favourite movies and series in clear, crisp, and vivid tones. It uses the Android TV operating system and comes preloaded with Netflix, YouTube, Amazon Prime, and Disney+ (note: subscriptions may be required), so you can stream your favourite content.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12_1GBy8 col-sm-6_9CRts col-md-4_2WnBH collapseColContainer_ueBNu\">\r\n<div class=\"pricingContainer_25k3c\">\r\n<div class=\"productPricingContainer_3gTS3\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'hisense-65-4k-uhd-hdr-led-android-smart-tv-65h78g-2020', '', '', '2020-12-08 22:44:59', '2020-12-08 22:44:59', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=120', 0, 'product', '', 0),
