(122, 1, '2020-12-08 22:49:02', '2020-12-08 22:49:02', '<strong>Play time</strong>\r\n\r\nDraw the blinds, dim the lights, and lose yourself in a world of dynamic interactive entertainment. The PlayStation 4 is your gateway to immersive gaming and endless possibilities. Find yourself on new worlds and embarking on grand adventures, from space-age swashbuckling to modern-day role-playing. Score the winning goal, drift across the finish line, or join with players from around the world to repel a horde of alien invaders. The choice is yours.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Exclusive games and expansive content</strong>\r\n\r\nThe PlayStation 4\'s game library features celebrated exclusive titles like The Last of Us Remastered, Bloodborne, God of War III, and the Uncharted series. Highly anticipated games that will be exclusive to the PS4 are always on the horizon as well.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWith a built-in Blu-ray player you can enjoy your collection of Full HD 1080p titles, and with Ethernet and WiFi connectivity options you can tap into your home network to access all the best movies, television shows, games, apps, and live sports. Stream instant content from Netflix, YouTube, Spotify or PlayStation Music. Access the PlayStation Store for the latest hot movies and exciting games.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Online multiplayer action with PlayStation Plus</strong>\r\n\r\nWhether teaming up with friends or taking on rivals, when you join PlayStation Plus you enter a sophisticated network of multiplayer experiences. Share Play lets you invite friends with PlayStation Plus access, wherever they are in the world, to join you for sessions of your favourite game, even if they don\'t own a copy. You get exclusive discounts and enjoy one membership across PS4, PS3, and PS Vita.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Stunning performance from a powerful console</strong>\r\n\r\nThe 1TB PlayStation 4 console features a next-generation processor and graphics engine, with an abundance of system memory, all of which powers a fast, fluid, visually stunning and immersive gameplay experience. Whether it\'s realistic game physics or inconceivable action, subtle detail or vibrant imagery, the PS4 is a platform for games to achieve new heights of authenticity and spectacle.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>DUALSHOCK 4 wireless controller</strong>\r\n\r\nThe DUALSHOCK 4 controller features improved ergonomics with evolved analog sticks and trigger buttons. Push the boundaries of play with a touch pad, integrated light bar, and internal speaker that offer additional ways to interact with games. A dedicated SHARE button makes it easy to showcase your achievements on Ustream or Facebook.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Please note: Console stand sold separately</strong>', 'PlayStation 4 1TB Console', '<div class=\"productDescription_2cw7s withChatInitiator_2G7gG\">\r\n<div class=\"description_39c9o\">Sleek and streamlined, the PlayStation 4 Slim opens the door to a world of immersive gaming and top-tier entertainment. Enjoy blockbuster storytelling presented in stunning Full HD 1080p and an online library full of exclusive content tailor-made for the PS4. Stream movies, tap into your favourite apps, and connect with your friends to embark on epic adventures together.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"initiator_17su9\" data-automation=\"blue-shirt-chat-container\">\r\n<div class=\"blueShirtsChatContainer_3uHKv\"></div>\r\n</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'playstation-4-1tb-console', '', '', '2020-12-08 22:49:02', '2020-12-08 22:49:02', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=122', 0, 'product', '', 0),
